V. Ethical Foundation and Sovereign Architecture 
The Omega-Governor functions as the meta-sovereign layer for ethical oversight, cross-sovereign coordination, authorization audit, rollback adjudication, and civilizational supervision; maintained by BEI Foundation via BEIGOV.com / .org and legally represented through BEIGovernor.com / .org. 
VI. Technological Embodiment and Standardization 
Operational platforms include BEICX (global clearing), BEISIGN (behavioral authorization stack), BEIINDEX/BEICREDIT (behavioral credit mapping), BEIMINT (behavior-to-value conversion), BEILEDGER (sovereign ledger), and domain modules such as BEIMED / BEIEDU / BEISTATE. 
All conform to BEI-STD and BEI-SEP, constituting the BEI-SES (Standard Essential System) - a globally standardizable, licensable, and verifiable BEI infrastructure. 
VII. Purpose - An Operating System for Civilization 
BEI enables sovereign participation for 8.3 billion people: identity becomes value, behavior becomes currency, and ethics becomes law. 
VIII. Declaration 
When human identity is governed scientifically and ethically, it becomes the highest infrastructure of civilization. This Charter marks the emergence of a new discipline - the unification of sovereignty, economy, and identity within a single ethical framework. 
